## 第二部分：自定义表格（展开行）

当表格需要展开行功能（如主从表）时，使用自定义 `<table>` 而非 DataTable。

### 完整功能清单

| 功能 | 必要性 | 说明 |
|------|--------|------|
| 文本搜索 | ✅ 必须 | 支持多字段模糊匹配 |
| 日期范围过滤 | ⭐ 推荐 | 使用 Calendar + Popover |
| 列排序 | ⭐ 推荐 | 点击表头切换升序/降序 |
| 全部展开/收起 | ⭐ 推荐 | 表头图标控制 |
| 展开行 | 按需 | 点击行展开子表格 |

### State 定义

```tsx
const [expandedRows, setExpandedRows] = React.useState<Record<number, boolean>>({});
const [searchTerm, setSearchTerm] = React.useState('');
const [fromDate, setFromDate] = React.useState<Date | undefined>();
const [toDate, setToDate] = React.useState<Date | undefined>();
const [sortField, setSortField] = React.useState<'field1' | 'field2' | null>('field1');
const [sortDirection, setSortDirection] = React.useState<'asc' | 'desc'>('desc');
```

### 过滤与排序逻辑

```tsx
const filteredData = React.useMemo(() => {
  let result = [...MOCK_DATA];

  // 文本搜索过滤
  if (searchTerm.trim()) {
    const term = searchTerm.toLowerCase();
    result = result.filter(
      (d) =>
        d.field1.toLowerCase().includes(term) ||
        d.field2.toLowerCase().includes(term)
    );
  }

  // 日期范围过滤
  if (fromDate || toDate) {
    result = result.filter((d) => {
      const itemDate = new Date(d.dateField);
      if (fromDate && itemDate < fromDate) return false;
      if (toDate && itemDate > toDate) return false;
      return true;
    });
  }

  // 排序
  if (sortField) {
    result.sort((a, b) => {
      let aVal = a[sortField];
      let bVal = b[sortField];
      if (aVal < bVal) return sortDirection === 'asc' ? -1 : 1;
      if (aVal > bVal) return sortDirection === 'asc' ? 1 : -1;
      return 0;
    });
  }

  return result;
}, [searchTerm, fromDate, toDate, sortField, sortDirection]);
```

### 全部展开/收起逻辑

```tsx
const isAllExpanded = React.useMemo(() => {
  return filteredData.length > 0 && filteredData.every((d) => expandedRows[d.id]);
}, [filteredData, expandedRows]);

const toggleAllRows = React.useCallback(() => {
  if (isAllExpanded) {
    setExpandedRows({});
  } else {
    const newExpanded: Record<number, boolean> = {};
    filteredData.forEach((d) => {
      newExpanded[d.id] = true;
    });
    setExpandedRows(newExpanded);
  }
}, [isAllExpanded, filteredData]);

const toggleRow = React.useCallback((id: number) => {
  setExpandedRows((prev) => ({
    ...prev,
    [id]: !prev[id],
  }));
}, []);
```

### 表格 Header 排序按钮

```tsx
<thead className="sticky top-0 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900">
  <tr className="border-b">
    <th className="w-10 px-2 py-3">
      <Button variant="ghost" size="icon" className="h-6 w-6" onClick={toggleAllRows}>
        {isAllExpanded ? <ChevronsDownUp className="h-4 w-4" /> : <ChevronsUpDown className="h-4 w-4" />}
      </Button>
    </th>
    <th className="px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-medium text-gray-600">
      <button className="inline-flex items-center hover:text-gray-900" onClick={() => handleSort('field1')}>
        字段名
        <SortIcon field="field1" />
      </button>
    </th>
  </tr>
</thead>
```

### 展开行渲染

```tsx
<tbody>
  {filteredData.map((item) => (
    <React.Fragment key={item.id}>
      <tr className="cursor-pointer border-b hover:bg-gray-50" onClick={() => toggleRow(item.id)}>
        <td className="px-2 py-3 text-center">
          <Button variant="ghost" size="icon" className="h-6 w-6">
            {expandedRows[item.id] ? <ChevronDown className="h-4 w-4" /> : <ChevronRight className="h-4 w-4" />}
          </Button>
        </td>
        <td>...</td>
      </tr>
      {expandedRows[item.id] && (
        <tr>
          <td colSpan={8} className="bg-gray-50 p-0">
            <div className="px-12 py-4">
              <div className="mb-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-600">子项明细</div>
              <div className="rounded-lg border bg-white">
                <table className="w-full text-sm">
                  <tbody>
                    {item.children.map((child) => <tr key={child.id}>...</tr>)}
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
      )}
    </React.Fragment>
  ))}
</tbody>
```

### 常用图标

| 功能 | 图标 | 导入 |
|------|------|------|
| 展开 | `ChevronRight` | `lucide-react` |
| 收起 | `ChevronDown` | `lucide-react` |
| 全部展开 | `ChevronsUpDown` | `lucide-react` |
| 全部收起 | `ChevronsDownUp` | `lucide-react` |
| 排序（未激活） | `ArrowUpDown` | `lucide-react` |
| 升序 | `ArrowUp` | `lucide-react` |
| 降序 | `ArrowDown` | `lucide-react` |

